{"tid":1218241,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[知己知彼］一齊熟讀 警隊條例tg group","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T04:38:26.000Z","uid":242779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3a2348e1e0ec742463198b9acccc36b926edbb","tid":1218241,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"呢幾日見到好多人為某幾個立法會議員既表現拍晒手<br />\n其實作為市民，係有責任認識法律，喺法庭上，唔識法律並不是一個辯護理由黎<br />\n<br />\n希望大家認識基本既法律知識後更懂得保護自己<br />\n<br />\n如果識講嘢又更加深入鑽研相關法律同警犬既工作作程序，希望大家勇於去保護其他較弱既兄弟姊妹，守望相助<br />\n<br />\n小弟其實都唔係識得多<br />\n但有些少法律知識，當然就不能同讀law既人比<br />\n希望可以用星星之火，令更多有料既人入黎將法律既一啲知識教比其他人<br />\n<br />\n授人以魚不如授人以漁<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MduKuBUM-DQKCYyDAJK2Sw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMduKuBUM-DQKCYyDAJK2Sw&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=af26cde3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MduKuBUM-DQKCYyDAJK2Sw</a>"},{"pid":"15fda74e8638e9429d36194a5c597d09f3503ba1","tid":1218241,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"89b58246d0dd8708f3edc387961b825a7269f0e4","tid":1218241,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db693171425ca070f2707d23247c460c9e3da3fa","tid":1218241,"uid":200235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n問極都會答，多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e2d3a89cd604e1070fed9d8eaa2a8e9736b0f3","tid":1218241,"uid":242779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家入左黎可以唔出聲，睇番上面啲history就得<br />\n有嘢問可以問，識既我盡力答"},{"pid":"dc55abcd703b969a8e745a4e8dcd9ec9feeae634","tid":1218241,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike